description:
The Blades of Khaine display the pinnacle of Aeldari prowess, featuring versatile Aspect Warriors from the Striking Scorpions, Dire Avengers, and Howling Banshees shrines. My Kill Team hail from Craftworld Ulthwé, and in this showcase post, I'll share a closer look.

The post Showcase: Aeldari Blades of Khaine Kill Team of Craftworld Ulthwé appeared first on Tale of Painters.
title: Showcase: Aeldari Blades of Khaine Kill Team of Craftworld Ulthwé
